  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  diagnosis of chronic cor pulmonale and admit to hospital

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pneumothorax or mediastinal emphysema

          -  active tuberculosis

          -  install a cardiac pacemaker

          -  acute cardiocerebrovascular events: acute myocardial infarction, acute myocarditis,
             severe arrhythmia, severe cerebrovascular accidents.

          -  pregnancies

          -  end-stage patients (expected survival time less than 6 months)
